  <div class="pane-content">
    <div class="seo-overview topics-colour0">
<div class="seo-body-content">
<a href="/topics/bitcoin"><h2 class="title">Bitcoin</h2></a>
<div class="seo-overview-description"><p>Bitcoin, released to the world in 2009 by a person or people called Satoshi Nakamoto, is not backed by a central bank or a government and is seen as an alternative payment system. In February 2013, Bitcoin went into the mainstream as a monetary crisis threatened to bankrupt Cyprus, seen as a safer bet. Early adopters of Bitcoin have been richly rewarded as the price has soared &ndash; in one case, a young Norwegian bought a house from an $850,000 windfall on a US$22 investment.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear:both;"></div>  </div>

  
