    <h1 itemprop="name headline" class="title" id="page-title">Investors fear HK$3b losses in closure of bitcoin trading company</h1>  </div>

  
  </div>
<div class="panel-separator"></div><div class="panel-pane pane-entity-field pane-node-field-subheading pos-6" >
    
  
  
  
  <div class="pane-content">
    <div class="field field-name-field-subheading field-type-text-long field-label-hidden clearfix">
    <div class="field-items">
                <div class="field-item even first last"><p>Claims of deception as 3,000 investors count cost of MyCoin closure</p>
